  "prompt": "How do I get call history for my Airtel prepaid number?",
  "response": "To access your call history for your Airtel prepaid number, you can use one of the following methods:\n\n### 1. **Using the Airtel Thanks App:**\n   - Download and install the Airtel Thanks app from the Google Play Store or Apple App Store if you don\u2019t have it already.\n   - Log in using your Airtel prepaid number.\n   - Once logged in, go to the \u2018Usage\u2019 or \u2018Account\u2019 section where you can find your call history.\n\n### 2. **Via SMS:**\n   - You can request a detailed bill (including call history) by sending an SMS.\n   - For example, you can send \"CALLHISTORY\" to 121 and follow any subsequent instructions.\n\n### 3. **Customer Service:**\n   - You can call Airtel customer care at 121 from your Airtel number. Follow the prompts to speak with an executive and request your call history.\n   - You can also visit a nearby Airtel store for assistance.\n\n### 4. **Online Portal:**\n   - Visit the Airtel website and log into your account if you have created one.\n   - Browse through the account settings to find your call history.\n\n### 5. **Contacting Airtel:**\n   - If you're unable to retrieve your call history through the app or SMS, you can always reach out to Airtel customer support through their official website or social media channels for help.\n\nMake sure you have the necessary details like your number and any other identification information ready when you contact customer support for a smoother experience.",
